  • Method Details

    • getClassName

      public String getClassName()
      Obtains a fully-qualified class name for this entry.
      E.g. if this entry has the path com/foo/bar/SomeClass.class it will return com.foo.bar.SomeClass

      If this entry does not represent a class file, it will either return a garbage string or throw.

      Returns:
      the fully-qualified class name.
      Throws:
      IndexOutOfBoundsException - You passed something that isn't a class and the function failed.
